Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,usual wager?\n- sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the, uh, loser cleans\nthe shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah.\n- okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,counting it in,\ni'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,3, 2...
